122
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,070
The way you put it,

123
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,330
I feel like one of those

124
00:06:18,540 --> 00:06:21,340
antique authentication experts on livestreams.

125
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:25,070
Okay, okay.

126
00:06:25,850 --> 00:06:26,920
If you ever

127
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,360
need anything,

128
00:06:29,030 --> 00:06:31,910
