00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,480
Did I?

296
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:19,720
Of...

297
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,960
of course not.

298
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,750
J,

299
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:27,320
you'd better show me

300
00:15:28,390 --> 00:15:32,360
how to walk in high heels without making any sound.

301
00:15:32,390 --> 00:15:34,120
Let's see if you can do it.

302
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:51,120
I was just worried something might happen to him.

303
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,670
That's why I rushed,

304
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:53,910
that's all.

305
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:57,120
Yet you suspect me.

306
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:00,440
You know that.

307
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,960
I've never suspected you.

308
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,000
Really?

309
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,610
You've never suspected me?

310
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:10,360
You never suspected me,

311
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:13,100
yet in Capital City,

312
00:16:14,210 --> 00:16:16,150
you had Taylor and the others secretly

313
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:18,670
plant bugs in Yang Guang's room without telling me.

314
00:16:18,670 --> 00:16:19,510
I trust you,

315
00:16:19,510 --> 00:16:20,710
but I don't trust him.

316
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:23,030
Fine, then.

317
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,870
I request to officially withdraw

318
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:28,130
from this mission starting today, okay?

319
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:38,200
You secured our contracts with Huaze and Taiyu.

320
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:43,240
The next phase of the mission is about to start.

321
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,250
You can't leave.

322
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,270
I can't leave.

323
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,880
If I don't leave, what do you want me to do?

324
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,480
I've followed your instructions

325
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,670
step by step.

326
00:16:52,920 --> 00:16:53,880
I've done my best

327
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:55,590
to complete every task you've assigned to me.

328
00:16:55,590 --> 00:16:57,840
And in the end, all I get in return is your suspicion.

329
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:58,720
If you were me,

330
00:16:58,720 --> 00:16:59,920
what would you think?

331
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:03,000
I just want to remind you

332
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:06,510
to never forget who you are at any time.

333
00:17:08,890 --> 00:17:10,109
I told you when you first

334
00:17:10,109 --> 00:17:11,569
joined the organization:

335
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:15,680
being swayed by emotions is taboo.

336
00:17:19,550 --> 00:17:20,310
To be honest,

337
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,550
I've really been

338
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,819
a bit concerned about you lately.

339
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,160
About what?

340
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:30,110
I trained you myself.

341
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:32,960
I know you're the most excellent agent.

342
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,290
But people have emotions.

343
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,210
Yang Guang saved your life.

344
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,720
It's natural for you to develop

345
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,930
some feelings for him.

346
00:17:40,930 --> 00:17:41,970
You also believe

347
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:44,060
that you can control those emotions.

348
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:46,720
But in the history of espionage,

349
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:50,810
there are countless cases where fake feelings became real.

350
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:51,790
So,

351
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:54,960
I want to remind you sincerely.

352
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:58,160
You must put the bigger picture first.

353
00:17:59,350 --> 00:18:02,240
You must not fall into emotional entanglements.

354
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:05,750
I know.

355
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:10,750
But Yang Guang is also an elite agent.

356
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:13,070
If I act in front of him,

357
00:18:13,070 --> 00:18:15,070
there's a high risk I'll be exposed.

358
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:16,230
Only sincerity

359
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,370
is the best weapon to deal with him.

360
00:18:26,030 --> 00:18:28,230
That's exactly what I'm worried about.

361
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:32,640
Fine.

362
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:37,070
I'll give you four options:

363
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:38,400
First,

364
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,400
maintain the status quo.

365
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:43,160
Second, I'll ignore him.

366
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:46,460
Third, completely win him over.

367
00:18:47,270 --> 00:18:48,750
Fourth, kill him.

368
00:18:49,350 --> 00:18:50,350
Make your choice.

369
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:51,920
Once you've decided,

370
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:52,590
tell me,

371
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:54,320
and I'll execute it for you.

372
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:05,400
I need to

373
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:08,200
check with the boss first.

374
00:19:23,310 --> 00:19:24,880
Hello, who ordered a designated driver?

375
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:27,400
Hello, the last four digits are 3233. Thank you.

376
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:27,830
Okay.

377
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:49,350
[I'm on my way home]

378
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:58,350
That's the situation.

379
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:01,160
I'm very worried about Zhao.

380
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:03,420
This is not my concern.

381
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:05,200
I only care about the result.

382
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:07,000
Ask Zhao to get him.

383
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:10,400
She's never liked this tactic.

384
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:11,830
Now,

385
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:15,070
making her sacrifice like this...

386
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:17,720
I'm very worried.

387
00:21:18,630 --> 00:21:20,790
J, you know our plans.

388
00:21:21,070 --> 00:21:23,270
Sacrifices will be worthwhile.

389
00:21:23,830 --> 00:21:25,790
This is a critical point,

390
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,680
and we need to determine

391
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:30,270
if she's an enemy or an ally.

392
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:33,550
If she fails...

393
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:36,310
Then, she's no longer our ally,

394
00:21:36,590 --> 00:21:38,680
but an enemy to be eliminated.

395
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,830
The top priority now

396
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:23,200
is receiving the package.

397
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:26,280
Three pieces of equipment are already on the way,

398
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:29,070
and I've adjusted the delivery method.

399
00:23:29,350 --> 00:23:30,030
Why?

400
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:33,160
I've already prepared.

401
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,160
It's too risky to use the same method.

402
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:50,070
The three items will now be transported separately

403
00:23:50,310 --> 00:23:52,000
by air, sea,

404
00:23:52,130 --> 00:23:53,440
and land.

405
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:56,070
I'll send you the pick-up locations

406
00:23:56,090 --> 00:23:58,000
by encrypted email.

407
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:01,750
I'll come up with a new plan.

408
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,790
You got the gift?

409
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:21,590
I got it.

410
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:27,300
I've hidden it in a safe place.

411
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,920
No one will ever find it.

412
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,000
Good.

413
00:24:32,020 --> 00:24:34,950
It will be very helpful in critical moments.

414
00:24:48,810 --> 00:24:49,850
Okay, Boss.

415
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,160
Okay.

416
00:24:57,680 --> 00:25:00,480
I'll be ready to receive the package.

417
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,630
Good night, Boss.

418
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:49,270
J, what's wrong?

419
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:50,800
What is Yang Guang doing?

420
00:28:51,190 --> 00:28:53,750
It shows he arrived home 15 minutes ago.

421
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,270
He was pretty drunk.

422
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:57,240
He should be sleeping at home now.

423
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:59,370
Go to his home immediately to confirm.

424
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,120
Something happened?

425
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:04,040
I suspect that someone has sneaked into my house.

426
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,200
You suspect it's Yang Guang?

427
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:09,340
At least, we need to rule him out as a suspect.

428
00:29:11,370 --> 00:29:11,930
J, I...

429
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:14,200
I really think you're being way too paranoid.

430
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,000
Listen to me.

431
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,400
Go there now and check.

432
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:19,000
Also,

433
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:21,750
about the choice you asked me to make,

434
00:29:21,750 --> 00:29:23,350
I'll tell you my answer now.

435
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:25,670
I'll give you one week.

436
00:29:26,590 --> 00:29:28,030
Completely win him over.

437
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:54,840
Why do you always ask me to seduce Yang Guang?

438
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:56,240
What do you take me for?

439
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,570
I don't like doing this!

440
00:29:58,160 --> 00:30:00,510
Because you are the most familiar with him.

441
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:02,310
Only you can complete this task.

442
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:04,970
You're really strange today.

443
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:06,930
Why are you asking this question?

444
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:08,510
Didn't you say you would do whatever it takes

445
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:09,910
to complete the mission?

446
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:23,440
[File transfer in progress]

447
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:44,480
Okay, I'll be ready to receive the package.

448
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:55,030
Okay, I'll be ready to receive the package.

449
00:31:27,970 --> 00:31:37,080
[Find a way to tail Yang Guang tomorrow.
See where he goes and whom he meets.]

450
00:31:37,270 --> 00:31:44,290
[I was just about to tell you. They've completely uncovered my identity.
I'm being closely watched now. I can't move.]

451
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:56,370
[I trust your abilities. Don't let me down. Think about your future together.
The immigration process is underway.]

452
00:32:10,910 --> 00:32:15,630
[But I don't even know where Yang Guang will be tomorrow.
How can I follow him?]

453
00:32:15,910 --> 00:32:19,550
[I'll tell you his location tomorrow morning.]

454
00:32:22,600 --> 00:32:25,310
[Okay.]

455
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,270
Drive.

456
00:33:52,320 --> 00:33:53,250
Shoot, let's go.

457
00:34:36,750 --> 00:34:38,230
Hey, Boss, I've arrived.

458
00:34:38,770 --> 00:34:39,850
Zhao is here too.

459
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:42,360
Keep an eye on them.

460
00:34:42,969 --> 00:34:43,699
Got it.

461
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:57,200
[Besides watching Zhao Yaning, you also need to keep watching Yang Guang.
As soon as he leaves tomorrow, notify me immediately.]

462
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:40,360
[Yang Guang]

463
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,280
Yang Guang?

464
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:30,400
Yang Guang!

465
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:40,000
[Confirmed. Yang Guang is at home.]

466
00:36:44,310 --> 00:36:49,190
[I called him from outside his apartment. I can hear his phone ringing,
but he's not answering.]

467
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:53,070
[He passed out drunk, sleeping heavily.]

468
00:37:12,710 --> 00:37:14,920
[You must see him in person]

469
00:37:22,250 --> 00:37:23,160
Yang Guang?

470
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:26,630
Yang Guang?

471
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,030
Xiaoman,

472
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:39,860
give me your building management's number.

473
00:37:40,330 --> 00:37:41,440
Yang Guang drank too much tonight.

474
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,150
I'm worried,

475
00:37:42,150 --> 00:37:43,480
so I came to check on him.

476
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:45,320
I'm outside his door now.

477
00:37:45,550 --> 00:37:47,130
I can hear his phone ringing inside,

478
00:37:47,130 --> 00:37:48,460
but he's not answering.

479
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:50,400
I'm worried about him.

480
00:37:51,330 --> 00:37:54,280
But getting the building management's number won't help.

481
00:37:54,280 --> 00:37:56,320
They can't open his door either.

482
00:37:58,720 --> 00:38:01,100
Okay, I'll try calling him a few more times.

483
00:38:01,100 --> 00:38:02,630
If he still doesn't answer,

484
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:04,480
I'll have to call the police.

485
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:04,510
Hello?

486
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:06,840
Are you okay?

487
00:39:07,710 --> 00:39:08,480
I'm fine.

488
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:10,480
Don't worry.

489
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,840
Why didn't you answer my call?

490
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:14,960
I fell asleep.

491
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:15,960
I didn't hear it.

492
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,210
My phone wasn't near me.

493
00:39:19,150 --> 00:39:21,350
I brought over the hangover soup I made.

494
00:39:21,620 --> 00:39:22,670
No need, no need, no need.

495
00:39:22,670 --> 00:39:23,870
Don't worry about me.

496
00:39:24,670 --> 00:39:26,270
I'm right outside your door.

497
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:27,190
Open up.

498
00:39:30,230 --> 00:39:30,840
Okay.

499
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:49,360
Hi.

500
00:39:50,800 --> 00:39:51,480
Come in.

501
00:39:56,710 --> 00:39:57,770
Where's the light?

502
00:39:58,440 --> 00:39:59,440
Turn on the light.

503
00:40:25,550 --> 00:40:26,410
Drink the soup.

504
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:34,620
Thank you.

505
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:53,230
Your place is so messy.

506
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:56,000
When was the last time you did your laundry?

507
00:40:59,010 --> 00:41:00,070
Don't worry about it.

508
00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:02,200
I'll wash it myself tomorrow morning.

509
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:04,050
Just leave it alone, okay?

510
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:19,080
How did the coat end up like this?

511
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,400
How did you...

512
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:36,150
how did you mess up my coat like this?

513
00:41:36,590 --> 00:41:38,150
How can I wear it again?

514
00:41:45,030 --> 00:41:47,480
I really drank too much tonight.

515
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:50,510
I haven't drunk like that for a long time.

516
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:51,670
I blacked out.

517
00:41:53,130 --> 00:41:55,060
When I got home, the taxi driver

518
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:57,370
had to yell at me for ages to wake me up.

519
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:00,030
I can't drink like that anymore.

520
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,960
I really shouldn't drink like that again.

521
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:02,960
You drank so much,

522
00:42:03,030 --> 00:42:05,400
yet you still knew to put your clothes in the washing machine.

523
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:07,600
It's precisely because I drank too much

524
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:10,380
that I put my clothes in the washing machine.

525
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:12,150
You see? I normally don't do that.

526
00:42:12,150 --> 00:42:14,150
Please, just leave it alone, okay?

527
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:15,510
I'm begging you.

528
00:42:16,110 --> 00:42:18,170
Just go home and get some sleep, okay?

529
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:33,180
I'll go after the laundry is done.

530
00:42:38,230 --> 00:42:40,630
You didn't throw up in the bedroom, did you?

531
00:42:41,230 --> 00:42:42,150
No, I don't think so.
